    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Additive color screen films introduced by Agfa Company on the German market in 1916. There are two generations of this additive color screen process on film: Agfacolor-Film (1932-1934) and Agfacolor Ultra (1934-1938).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
